We have a great new today! Your favorite Disney princess Elsa has got pregnant and she is expected to deliver twins. She has started feeling a severe pain suddenly due to a tragedy that happened with her. It seems that she lost her balance and fell down on the ground. Oh girls, her pain is unbearable and she seeks for an urgent help! Are you able to give your precious helping hand to her? Join Pregnant Elsa Twins Birth game and get ready to provide her with the needful medical assistance!

Your objective in this doctor game for girls is to make sure that everything is ok with Elsa and her baby. Ambulance is on its way so try to take care of her until the medical bus arrives and takes her to the hospital. Once she reaches the hospital, get ready to take care of her twins. Check her twins are ok with the help of EKG machine! Use a pair of pliers and then start working on removing the splinter in her skin. It will be your responsibility to bandage her wound to get it healed timely in this html5 surgery game. Feel free to wipe the blood of her skin using a tissue paper!

Do not forget to give your princess the needful nutrients to help lessen her weakness after the incident. Calm her pain by giving her a pill safely and heal her swollen eyes with a pack of ice! Make sure that she is using a mask to restore the needful amount of oxygen in her body.  She and her twins also need an injection on time in order to protect them against any disease caused by an injection. You will see that now Elsa and her babies start feeling great. Good luck to take care of her along with her twins properly in this princess girls games that are free to play online on atmegame.com!
